summary: Jenna Marbles could post a video titled ‘Summoning Satan’ or ‘Performing blood rituals’ and we’d never fucking question it....
body: Jenna Marbles could post a video titled ‘Summoning Satan’ or ‘Performing blood rituals’ and we’d never fucking question it. We’re already like “Oh, she’s painting herself green today? Neat, lets watch.” and “Jeans chair? Alrighty, then.” Its just. We’ve all become so adjusted to seeing her videos over the years that we can’t remember what she originally did. We’ve become so used to her content that we barely even stop to think about it
